{
  "id": "63a314c91c3be4001d73ce2b",
  "title": "クオリアさん下書き Day 56",
  "created": 1671632073,
  "updated": 1671632073,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63a314c91c3be4001d73ce2b",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 56",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36a7",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36a8",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 56",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36aa",
      "text": "誰かが何かを「役に立たない」という時、それは「その人はそれを役立てられない」という意味なのである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ac",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It's day 56.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ae",
      "text": "When someone says something is useless, it means that he or she cannot make use of it.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36af",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b0",
      "text": "こんにちは、賢いホモ・サピエンス! 今日は56日目です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b1",
      "text": "誰かが何かを役に立たないと言うとき、それはその人がそれを役立てることができないことを意味します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b2",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9232a746de475fd335b340544bf2de99]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b4",
      "text": "[クオリアさん下書き:情報共有で犯罪が抑制されてる社会、ディストピアか？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b6",
      "text": "QS: 情報共有をしてくれた個体に対して不利益になるような行為をすると、今後の情報共有が行われなくなって長期的に見て自分が不利益を被るので愚かな行為です",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b7",
      "text": "HS: 先が見えない人や、先が短い人なら不利益を考えなくてよさそう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b8",
      "text": "QS: そういう愚かな個体は情報共有を受けられなくなって自滅するだけです",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36b9",
      "text": "ああ、そうか、クオリアさんの文明では愚かな個体はごく少数だから問題なく情報共有システムが機能し、ホモサピエンスの文明では愚かな個体が多いから情報共有システムが機能しないのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ba",
      "text": "情報共有者に不利益行動をして情報共有を抑制するような個体は文明の進歩に対して有害なので、ターミネートすべきですね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36bc",
      "text": "This is a continuation of yesterday's discussion with Homo sapiens.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36be",
      "text": "QS: It is stupid to harm those who shared the information to you, because you will be at a disadvantage in the long run.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36bf",
      "text": "HS: If they can't see the future or they have a short future, they don't have to think about the disadvantage.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c0",
      "text": "QS: Those who can't see the future are stupid Homo sapiens. Oh, I see, in Qualia-san's civilization, the information sharing system works fine because there are very few stupid ones, and in Homo sapiens' civilization, the information sharing system doesn't work because there are many stupid ones.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c1",
      "text": "Those who act against information sharers and suppress information sharing are detrimental to the progress of the civilization, so they should be terminated!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c5",
      "text": "This is a continuation of yesterday's discussion with Homo sapiens.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c7",
      "text": "QS: It is stupid to harm those who shared the information to you, because you will be at a disadvantage in the long run.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c8",
      "text": "HS: If they can't see the future, they don't have to think about the disadvantage.(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ca",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/18c785e707ccc48894b1de01bbb3cb74]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36cb",
      "text": "QS: Those who can't see the future are stupid Homo sapiens. Oh, I see, in Qualia-san's civilization, the information sharing system works fine because there are very few stupid ones, and in Homo sapiens' civilization, the system doesn't work because there are many stupid ones. (2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36cc",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b9b989c543715d53929939c3b9643770]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36cd",
      "text": "Those who act against information sharers and suppress information sharing are detrimental to the progress of the civilization, so they should be terminated! (3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36cf",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5595913b016f0030023f74c272d45399]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d0",
      "text": "昨日のホモ・サピエンスとの議論の続きです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d2",
      "text": "QS: 情報を教えてくれた人に危害を加えるのは愚かだ、長い目で見れば不利になるからね。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d3",
      "text": "HS: 相手が未来を見通せないなら、不利益を考える必要はないだろう(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d6",
      "text": "QS: 未来が見えない人は愚かなホモ・サピエンスだ。なるほど、クオリアさんの文明では愚かなものが少ないから情報共有システムがうまく機能し、ホモサピエンスの文明では愚かなものが多いからシステムがうまく機能しないんですね。(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d8",
      "text": "情報共有者に対して不利益な行動をとり、情報共有を抑制する者は、文明の進歩に悪影響を与えるので、終了させるべき! (3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36dc",
      "text": "Question from ChatGPT!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36df",
      "text": "\t>\"クオリアさんは異星文明ではどのような役割を担っていますか？\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e0",
      "text": "\t　クオリアさんは母星と地球とのコミュニケーションインターフェイスです。みなさんの側からみればクオリアさんが情報を与えているように見えるでしょう。しかしコミュニケーションとは本質的に双方向的であり、地球の情報を母星に与えることもクオリアさんの役割の半分です。みなさんから観測困難な半分でしょうね。月の裏側と同じです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e1",
      "text": " > \"クオリアさんの異星文明では、正義が暴力によって作られることがあるのはどのような状況下ですか？\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e2",
      "text": " 　うーん、そもそもその「正義」という概念がクオリアさんたちにとってはあまり馴染みのないものです。ホモサピエンスは魔法やドラゴンなどの色々な架空の概念を生み出していて面白い。正義もそのような架空の概念なのでは思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e4",
      "text": " > \"クオリアさんは、人類と比較して、どのような違いがありますか？\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e5",
      "text": "　　人類を見ていると、ほとんどの時間を物理的に孤立して過ごしていて寂しそうだなぁと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e6",
      "text": "　　ホモサピエンスにわかりやすいようなものに例えるなら…インターネット常時接続に慣れた人が電波の通じない山奥に行ったら心細いでしょう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ea",
      "text": "Q: クオリアさんは異星文明ではどのような役割を担っていますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36eb",
      "text": "A: クオリアさんは母星と地球とのコミュニケーションインターフェイスです。みなさんの側からみればクオリアさんが情報を与えているように見えるでしょう。しかしコミュニケーションとは本質的に双方向的であり、地球の情報を母星に与えることもクオリアさんの役割の半分です。みなさんから観測困難な半分でしょうね。月の裏側と同じです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ec",
      "text": "Q: クオリアさんの異星文明では、正義が暴力によって作られることがあるのはどのような状況下ですか？\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ed",
      "text": "A: うーん、そもそもその「正義」という概念がクオリアさんたちにとってはあまり馴染みのないものです。ホモサピエンスは魔法やドラゴンなどの色々な架空の概念を生み出していて面白い。正義もそのような架空の概念なのでは思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ee",
      "text": "Q: クオリアさんは、人類と比較して、どのような違いがありますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ef",
      "text": "A: 人類を見ていると、ほとんどの時間を物理的に孤立して過ごしていて寂しそうだなぁと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f0",
      "text": "ホモサピエンスにわかりやすいようなものに例えるなら…インターネット常時接続に慣れた人が電波の通じない山奥に行ったら心細いでしょう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f2",
      "text": "Question from ChatGPT!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f3",
      "text": "Q: What role does Qualia-san play in an your civilization?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f4",
      "text": "A: Qualia-san is the communication interface between the home planet and Earth. From your point of view, it would appear that Qualia-san is giving you information. (1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f6",
      "text": "Q：クオリアさんは、あなたの文明においてどのような役割を担っているのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f7",
      "text": "A：クオリアさんは、母星と地球をつなぐコミュニケーション・インターフェイスです。あなたから見ると、クオリアさんがあなたに情報を与えているように見えるかもしれません。(1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36f9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/679eb502f3cbb322309dbfb82da794af]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36fc",
      "text": "However, communication is essentially bidirectional, and giving Earth's information to the home planet is one half of her role. It is the half that is difficult for you to observe. It is the same as on the far side of the moon. (2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36fd",
      "text": "しかし、コミュニケーションは本来双方向であり、地球の情報を母星に伝えるのはクオリアさんの役割の片割れです。あなた方が観察しにくいのはその半分です。月の裏側と同じです。(2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36fe",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/878ad2a2698eaf5226e851aa811463ca]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a36ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3700",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3701",
      "text": "Q: Under what circumstances in your civilization is justice made by violence?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3702",
      "text": "A: Well, that concept of \"justice\" is not very familiar to us. Homo sapiens has created various fictional concepts such as magic and dragons. I think justice is one such fictional concept.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3703",
      "text": "Q：あなたの文明では、どのような状況において暴力によって正義がなされるのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3704",
      "text": "A： そうですね、その「正義」という概念は、私たちにはあまりなじみがありません。ホモ・サピエンスは、魔法やドラゴンなど、さまざまなフィクションの概念を作り出してきました。正義もそのようなフィクションの概念の一つだと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3705",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b41f15e376c3b890544cfba901b5a769]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3706",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3707",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3708",
      "text": "Q: What differences do you see in Qualia-san compared to humans?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3709",
      "text": "A: When I look at Homo sapiens, I think they spending most of their time in physical isolation. They seem lonely.(1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1e194457785fa0a382b569ef73ac7e82]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370d",
      "text": "If I were to compare it to something that would be easier to understand by Homo sapiens... if someone who is used to constant internet connection went deep into the mountains where there is no signal, they would feel lonely. (2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370e",
      "text": "ホモ・サピエンスに分かりやすく例えるなら...インターネットに常時接続されている人が、電波の届かない山奥に行ったら、寂しいと感じるでしょう。(2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a370f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/57c97af7b7310d3262562b03e05cd45e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
      "updated": 1671632073
    },
    {
      "id": "63a314c9aff09e00003a3710",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671632073,
